title: M56 closed in both directions after tanker overturns
text:
Cheshire Police @cheshirepolice Follow #M56 : Full closure in both directions between junctions 11(Daresbury) and 14 (Hapsford) please avoid the area if possible
16:17 - 20 Oct 2015 Retweet Reply Favourite The M56 has been closed in both directions after a tanker overturned on the Eastbound carriageway.
There are reports of very slow traffic due to the overturned vehicle between Junction 14 for the A5117 at Hapsford and Junction 12 for the A557 (Runcorn).
Last updated Tue 20 Oct 2015 Travel Cumbria Cheshire Manchester Lancashire Liverpool Merseyside Greater Manchester
